dct_title_s: Panama Canal & Central Panama : scale 1:300,000 / 1:100,000 / Lan Joyce, editor in chief.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by gradient and spot heights. Depth shown by bathymetric tints on Central Panama map. Shows transportation hubs, lodging places, tourist attractions, and points of interest. Includes indexes and text. Includes Panama City transit map on alternate panel.
